node.text:
We had the best time this weekend at the #NYTFoodFestival eating incredible food from @leonellinyc @morgansternsnyc @marcforgione and more!
The @nytimes & @nytlive brought together some of NYC’s best restaurants and vendors for two special days of food in Bryant Park and we already can’t wait until next year 😝
#newforkcity

node.text:
We partnered with @jokrnyc to give away the ultimate snack pack featuring treats from @mastchocolate, @mikeshothoney, @vanleeuwenicecream, & $150 to use in the JOKR app! Follow their page to enter & to see all the details.
In the meantime, we’ll be perfecting our ice cream sundae bar at home with all these goodies that we got delivered in under 15 minutes! 🍦 #ad
#newforkcity
